*Veći* deo grada je u ruševinama. (Most of the city is in ruins.)

*Veća* čast mi je da Vam pomognem. (It is a greater honor for me to help you.)

*Većim* delom, ona je zadovoljna sa svojim životom. (For the most part, she is satisfied with her life.)

*Većim* je uspehom promovisala svoj brend. (She promoted her brand with greater success.)

*Veće* vreme uloženo u rad je donelo dobre rezultate. (Greater time invested in work yielded good results.)

*Većoj* meri je to bilo korisno. (To a greater extent, that was useful.)